# id: CentralDirectoryFileHeader -> private Calendar decodeMsDosFormatDateTime(long date, long time)
commentText: Decode MS-DOS Date Time details. See_mindprod.com/jgloss/zip.html for_more details of the format._@param date the date part_@param time the time part_@return a {@link Calendar} containing the decoded date.
codeText: private Calendar decodeMsDosFormatDateTime(long date, long time) {_		int year = (int) ((date >> 9) & 0x7F) + 1980__		int month = (int) ((date >> 5) & 0xF) - 1__		int day = (int) (date & 0x1F)__		int hours = (int) ((time >> 11) & 0x1F)__		int minutes = (int) ((time >> 5) & 0x3F)__		int seconds = (int) ((time << 1) & 0x3E)__		return new GregorianCalendar(year, month, day, hours, minutes, seconds)__	}
